<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>约饭</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="onepage">
            <div class="onepage-bg" id="onepage"></div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="title-text">
                        <div class="col-md-12 headfontsize">
                            <h1 class="headh1content">
                                一顿饭，创造一段新关系
                            </h1>
                            <p>
                                用餐廳、話題、興趣...等資訊，來尋找跟你志同道合的朋友一起吃飯吧！</p>
                            <!-- <h3 class="headh3content">
                轻松聊  &nbsp 美食 &nbsp  人生梦想 &nbsp 旅行 &nbsp 马上出发
              </h3> -->
                            <p class="btn-app-store">
                                <%= link_to("发起约饭", new_post_path(@post), class: "btn btn-danger btn-lg", style: "background-color:#f01d67;") %>
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="twopage">
            <div class="twopage-text">
                <h1 class="twopage-text-h1">
                    全部约饭
                </h1>
            </div>





         <!-- 这里是引用的partial文件，达到加载更多的约饭 -->
         <div class=center>
            <div id="content">
                <%= render(partial: 'post') %>
            </div>
          </div>
            <div class="center">
                   <!-- 判断页数 -->
                <% unless @posts.current_page == @posts.total_pages %>
                <p id="view-more">
                    <%= link_to('载入更多约饭', url_for(page: @posts.current_page + 1), remote: true,
                           class: "btn btn-success btn-lg") %>
                </p>
                <% end %>
            </div>
            <!-- 这里是引用的partial文件，达到加载更多的约饭 -->








        <div class="threepage">
            <div class="threepage-bg" id="threepage">
                <div class="threepagecontent">
                    <div class="threepagetext">
                        <h3>「Eatgether一起吃」利用聚餐交友功能，徹底結合「飲食」與「社交」，為餐廳創造無限的可能性！
                            <br><br>只等有缘的你
                        </h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="bottompage col-md-4 ">
                        <div class="threepage-weixin">
                            <a href="#">
                                <img src="http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/006tNc79jw1f9t19or41kj3069069wec.jpg" style="width: 100px;">
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bottompage col-md-4 ">
                        <div class="threepage-weixin">
                            <a href="#">
                                <img src="http://ww2.sinaimg.cn/large/006tNc79jw1f9t19oq9rvj3069069jrf.jpg" style="width: 100px;">
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bottompage col-md-4 ">
                        <div class="threepage-weixin">
                            <a href="#">
                                <img src="http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/large/006tNc79jw1f9t2mm8664j305o05odfq.jpg" style="width: 100px;">
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </body>
</html>
